episodes.title: The Founder of Chess.com Was Raised in a Cult *book review*
episodes.description:
Hi friends ✨

I recently finished reading Dark Squares by Danny Rensch, the co-founder of Chess.com, and it wasa ride. It’s part memoir, part chess history, and part deep dive into trauma, obsession, and self discovery.

I’m not going to spoil anything here, just share my honest thoughts and feelings.

If you’re into chess, psychology, or just inspiring life stories, this one might surprise you.♟️

🧸Chapters:

0:00 – Introduction
1:15 – Danny Rensch & “Dark Squares”
4:40 – Book Reflections
9:45 – Chess.com & Hans Niemann Scandal
13:50 – Final Thoughts & Review
